<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_442" id="220r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_442_r1l26">Thomas von <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_442_r1l27"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt Thomas von <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_442_r1l28">wıe eẅch geſagt ſey daʒ Jr vnd das eẅr . vor vns vnd den <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_442_r1l29">niht ſıcher ſeyt . von des <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ eẅr <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_442_r1l30"><expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat da eẅr knecht bey <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyn etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_443" id="220v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_443_r1l1"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Alſo tun wır eẅch ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vnd das eẅr . <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_443_r1l2">kein ſchad <expan>geſchehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt vnd hinfür kein ſchad geſchıht / vor vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_443_r1l3">vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſıcher ſüllt ſein on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>feſtu<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_443_r1l4"><expan>aſce<ex>n</ex>ſıo<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nj</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_442" id="220r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Thomas von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst. Thomas von
                            <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch gesagt sey, daz
                        ir und das ewr vor uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht sicher
                        seyt von des <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ewr
                            <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> uns und den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, da ewr knecht bey
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyn etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <pb facs="#facs_443" id="220v"/><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Also tun wir ewch zu
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir und das ewr,
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns kein schad
                                <expan>geschehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ist und hinfür kein schad
                        geschiht, vor uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sicher süllt sein
                        on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>festu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>asce<ex>n</ex>sio<ex>n</ex>is</expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan>.</ab>
</div>
